_json.gridTitle: Spicy Corn Palak recipe, Microwave Subzis Recipes
_json.description: From pizzas and pastas to pulaos and subzis, corn and spinach are an ever successful duo as they complement each other very well in flavour, texture and appearance. In this delectable Spicy Corn Palak recipe, they are combined with onions, tomato puree and other spice enhancers to make a truly mouth-watering subzi.
